	<p align="justify">Please fill out the fields below to register for the fall advanced league
	draft.
	Please note that except for comments/special requests,
	<b>all</b> fields are required.</p>
	<p align="justify">You should
	receive a confirmation email following the completion and submission of your
	registration.  <b>If you do not receive this email</b>, please ensure that your
	email address is spelled correctly and resubmit your registration with
	your corrected address if needed.  If you still do not receive a confirmation
	email, please contact <b>webmaster<img src=at.gif>hawaiiultimate.com</b>
	for further assistance.</p>
	<p><i>[Note: Because all games will be played on the same fields
	during the same time frame, couples will not be drafted together.
	Very rare exceptions may be made for extreme circumstances, which
	you should explain below. If you really want to play with someone,
	become a captain and pick them for your team!]</i></p>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td><center><table border=0>
    <tr><td colspan=3><hr></td></tr>
    <tr><td>First Name</td> <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td> <td><input name ="firstname" type="text"></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Last Name</td> <td></td> <td><input name="lastname" type="text"></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Email</td> <td></td> <td><input name="email" type="text"></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Phone Number</td> <td></td> <td><input name="phone" type="text"></td></tr>
    <tr><td>Gender</td> <td></td> <td><input name="gender" type="radio" value="Male"> Male&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                <input name="gender" type="radio" value="Female"> Female</td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Commitment Level:  Games will be played on Wednesday nights at Palolo 
	District Park, starting at 7:00 p.m., with one game per night. There will be 
	nine nights of regular league season plus one night of semis and finals. The 
	season will begin in the first week of October and run until the first or 
	second week in December. Please realistically rate the number of nights that 
	you will be able to attend:<br>
	<table border=0>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="100%"></td><td>100% (all ten games, come hell or high water)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="90%"></td><td>90% (all games, barring any unforeseen circumstances)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="80%"></td><td>80% (this will be my Wednesday night priority)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="70%"></td><td>70% (I know I'll be gone for at least a week or two)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="60%"></td><td>60%</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="50%"></td><td>50% (I love ultimate but life calls)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="40%"></td><td>40%</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="30%"></td><td>30% (Wed nights are tough, but maybe just maybe)</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="20%"></td><td>20%</td></tr>
	<tr><td><input name="commitment" type="radio" value="10%"></td><td>10% (not sure if I can play at all but would like to be drafted on a team just in case)</td></tr>
	</table>
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Leadership
      <br><input name="leadership" type="radio" value="No">Don't make me a captain
      <br><input name="leadership" type="radio" value="Maybe">Wouldn't mind being a captain
      <br><input name="leadership" type="radio" value="Yes">Excited to be a captain (yes, I am volunteering!)
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan=3><hr><p><b>Player Ratings</b>:
	Players will be drafted based on "draft scores". To get your draft score, 
	just add up the 5 numbers. The maximum is 35. For this advanced league, we 
	recommend a minimum of 5-5-3-3-3 or a 19. Don't quite make the cut? Try
	<b><a href=league.asp>city
	league</a></b> or <b><a href=recleague.asp>rec night</a></b>.
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Experience<br>
	<table border=0>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="1"></td><td>[1] Never played before</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="2"></td><td>[2] Played some pickup or rec night</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="3"></td><td>[3] Played one season of city league</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="4"></td><td>[4] Played 2 to 4 seasons of league</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="5"></td><td>[5] Played 5+ seasons of league or in Hopu</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="6"></td><td>[6] Played in Kaimana once or Hopu multiple times</td>
	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="7"></td><td>[7] Played in Club Regionals, or in Club Sectionals or Kaimana multiple times</td>
