	<tr><td><input name="experience" type="radio" value="10"></td><td>[10] Played in Club Nationals on an elite team or multiple times</td>
	</table>
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Skills<br>
	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="1">[1] Just learning to throw<br>
	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="2">[2] Decent backhand or forehand<br>
	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="3">[3] Familiar with stack offense (and #2)<br>
