	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="6">[6] Occasional break mark throws<br>
	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="7">[7] Strong backhand and forehand<br>
	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="8">[8] Strong handler (both stack and zone offense)<br>
