	<input name="skills" type="radio" value="10">[10] Accurate break mark throws and hucks<br>
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Speed<br>
	<input name="speed" type="radio" value="1">[1] Little on the slow side<br>
	<input name="speed" type="radio" value="2">[2] Average<br>
	<input name="speed" type="radio" value="3">[3] Good<br>
	<input name="speed" type="radio" value="4">[4] Pretty fast<br>
	<input name="speed" type="radio" value="5">[5] One of the fastest on the field
    </td></tr>

    <tr><td colspan="3"><br>Athleticism<br>
	<input name="athleticism" type="radio" value="1">[1] Can't run or jump, but love to play!<br>
	<input name="athleticism" type="radio" value="2">[2] Average<br>
